<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Set of Oracle EPM Cloud groups to be loaded in IIQ</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle EPM Cloud application team to provide the list of roles</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle EPM Cloud SOD matrix</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle EPM Cloud application team to provide the SOD matrix</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
